{      ADVANCING A 1NT OVERCALL      
A SUMMARY}
^-|ht|e|fp||at|
Many partnerships play ^*BSystem on - Double Stolen Bid or ^*N"Front Of the Card" (FOC) after a notrump overcall. This is similar to the responses to opening notrump bids are.

^C 3NT - To play 
^C 3@H/3@S - Slam invitational 
^C 3@C/3@D - Invitational, 6-card suit 
^C 2NT - Invitational 
^C 2@S - Relay to 3@C (to play in 3@C or 3@D) 
^C 2@H - Jacoby transfer to spades 
^C 2@D - Jacoby transfer to hearts 
^C 2@C - Stayman|PG||NT||
